    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-03-01T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-03-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="213" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d213">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Stevens</persName> to
                                    Mr. <persName type="to">Foster</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Honolulu</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-03-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 1, 1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>All quiet throughout archipelago. Protectorate is preventing pressure
                                of the British minister. The Japanese representatives telegraphed
                                Government January 19. Japanese ship <hi rend="italic">Naniwa</hi>
                                arrived February 23. <hi rend="italic">Kongo</hi> arrived January
                                28. It is believed that the Japanese representative who arrived
                                November 28 is urged by the British minister. It is believed that
                                the British ship <hi rend="italic">Warspite</hi> has been ordered
                                here to provide for contingencies. It is advisable to send here at
                                once the most powerful American ship available. I have sent
                                particulars by mail.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stevens.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
